long_description: at shepherd electric supply, our mission is to provide excellence in service, pricing, and products, every time. our mission drives us to be the most successful electrical distributor in our markets, and to earn the reputation as the best employer in the area. we pride ourselves on excellent service, low cost and quality products. founded in 1892, shepherd electric supply is the oldest wholesale electrical distributor in the baltimore/washington area. our experienced and knowledgeable sales staff is ready to service your every need and exceed your expectations. we have specialized divisions to handle a diverse group of customers including commercial construction, lighting and switchgear projects, commercial facilities, facility management, industrials, oems, and government organizations. we currently have four locations: baltimore, laurel (formerly beltsville), frederick (md), and sterling (va). we also have an affiliate company, shepherd electric supply of washington dc, llc. the company partners with general electric, also founded in 1892.
